<span id="freeTextContainer13488498465887863751">Revelations, the revealing of things..that is exactly what you will find in the second installment of Ruin. Pieces of the puzzle are being put together and we are getting better acquainted with our favorite characters from The Waking. In this continuation Ruin and Isadore find themselves assigned tasks that seem to take them back to Isadore&apos;s past in order to find answers to this mental block that she apparently has up against Ruin and Ruin is ever determined to break them down. So get geared up</span>
  <span id="freeText13488498465887863751" style="display:none">Revelations, the revealing of things..that is exactly what you will find in the second installment of Ruin. Pieces of the puzzle are being put together and we are getting better acquainted with our favorite characters from The Waking. In this continuation Ruin and Isadore find themselves assigned tasks that seem to take them back to Isadore's past in order to find answers to this mental block that she apparently has up against Ruin and Ruin is ever determined to break them down. So get geared up for this phenomenal and unique story line with all the twists and turns to go along with the familiar writing style of Lucian Bane.<br /><br />Things are heating up between Ruin and Isadore in this installment of the book and we have a front row seat! The banter between them is downright hilarious, the adventures from his "tasks" will keep you on the edge of your seat and the sexual chemistry/tension is off the charts. Lucian really brings these characters to life, no matter what genre or what the story line is, he will keep you entertained!</span>
