        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1088862809" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3636378816030663651"><b>Thought provoking and magical - I&apos;m definitely RUINED!!!</b><br/><br/>Ruin and Isadore return with a vengeance!!!!!<br/>This book picks up exactly where Ruin: The Awakening left off.<br/><br/>Once again Lucian Bane has allowed his words to speak for themselves. Diving back into the world of Ruin and Isadore is like meeting up with old friends and renewing that relationship.<br/><br/>Revelations looks deeper into the relationship between Ruin and Izzy. As the title states, things are being revealed and puzzles pieces are being put tog</span>
  <span id="freeText3636378816030663651" style="display:none"><b>Thought provoking and magical - I'm definitely RUINED!!!</b><br /><br />Ruin and Isadore return with a vengeance!!!!!<br />This book picks up exactly where Ruin: The Awakening left off.<br /><br />Once again Lucian Bane has allowed his words to speak for themselves. Diving back into the world of Ruin and Isadore is like meeting up with old friends and renewing that relationship.<br /><br />Revelations looks deeper into the relationship between Ruin and Izzy. As the title states, things are being revealed and puzzles pieces are being put together. There are still gaps to be plugged up, however I'm sure that Mr Bane will no doubt cover these further along the track. The interactions between these two characters is written with superb brilliance. They are unlike any others I have read. Their banter will have you laughing in the aisles, or have you so frustrated that you want to clip the pair of them under the ear. And the sex...well no one can write a sex scene like Lucian. Hot and heavy ....your temperature will be soaring.<br /><br />Ruin and Isadore are face with revelations from their past - some good, some not so good. It is a journey of discovery. New tasks are given and a judgement is to be made. Ruin must learn from the beginning once again, but this time with Isadore's help. <br /><br />This couple is so hot together, that my Kindle almost melted at their passion.<br />One again Mr Bane you have excelled yourself - thank you<br />There's humour, intrigued and passion throughout the entire book<br /><br />This series is definitely entertaining. I dare you to put this book down before you finish it .... I bet you can't. The words are addictive and you just NEED to know what is going to happen next.<br /><br />Read and reviewed for Reading Is Our Satisfaction.<br /><br />FIVE "RUINED" STARS</span>
  <a data-text-id="3636378816030663651" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
